{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceAndAssign\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">synthInstanceAndAssign</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x </span><span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Helper function for instantiating a type class `type`, and\nthen using the result to perform `isDefEq x val`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceAndAssign","kind":"def","line":79,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceAndAssign","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L79-L85"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">synthInstance</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance","kind":"def","line":74,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L74-L77"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">synthInstance?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance?","kind":"def","line":69,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstance?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L69-L72"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.registerInstance\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">registerInstance</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type </span><span class=\"fn\">inst</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">SymM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Registers `inst` as **the** instance for `type`. `synthInstance?` returns it without\nrunning typeclass resolution, making `inst` the canonical representative for `type`.\nIntended for satellite modules that construct instances for types they create themselves\n(e.g., `grind linarith`'s envelope type `IntModule.OfNatModule.Q`).\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.registerInstance","kind":"def","line":60,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.registerInstance","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L60-L67"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceMeta?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">synthInstanceMeta?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceMeta?","kind":"def","line":53,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.synthInstanceMeta?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L53-L58"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.getBuiltinInstance?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">getBuiltinInstance?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">type</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Some modules in grind use builtin instances defined directly in core (e.g., `lia`).\nUsers may provide nonstandard instances that are definitionally equal to the ones in core.\nGiven a type, such as `HAdd Int Int Int`, this function returns the instance defined in\ncore.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.getBuiltinInstance?","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.getBuiltinInstance?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SynthInstance.lean#L44-L51"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM","Lean.Meta.SynthInstance"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.SynthInstance"}